        (112476, 'Dylan Minnette', '1996-12-29', 'Dylan Christopher Minnette was born in Evansville, Indiana in 1996.  Scouted by an agent in Chicago, Dylan began work on commercial modeling  and acting at the age of 7. He later relocated to Los Angeles, CA to  continue his acting career.

