In the spring of 2008, Yu directed The Odd Couple for the Vancouver Asian Canadian Theatre company.

As of 2010-2011, Raugi teaches acting courses at New Image College of Fine Arts in Vancouver, British Columbia. He also teaches the summer Young Shakespearian program which Bard puts on every year for youth ages eight to eighteen.', 'Montréal, Québec, Canada', 1, '/t2HL83bmp7t1p5Z9xxblCkV2X3q.jpg'),
