        (139635, 'Stuart Davidson', '1972-06-30', 'Stuart Davidson was born on June 30, 1972 in Watford, Hertfordshire, England as Daniel Stuart Davidson. His ancestry is mostly English, Greek Cypriot, and Scottish. He is an actor, known for Mission: Impossible - Fallout (2018), Miss Peregrine''s Home for Peculiar Children (2016), and Far from the Madding Crowd (2015).

