 She later became engaged to producer Michael Mailer, son of writer Norman Mailer, but Mailer later called off the engagement for unexplained reasons to marry someone else. Maples is now a confirmed spiritualist and single mom. Marla is currently host of her own radio show on Contact Talk Radio http://www.contacttalkradio.com the first Friday of every month', 'Dalton, Georgia, USA', 1, '/sealX9DeWcPWDSZVdr7vfPVLumw.jpg'),
