Raised in Buffalo, New York,she got her start in modelingbefore making the transition to acting in 2001 with a role on the soap opera, Port Charles. That part on the daytime drama led to guest appearances in several other series, including Joey, Girlfriends, 90210, and as Anna Schick in The Young &amp; The Restless.', 'U.S.A', 1, '/oYHe5OXY0qltXJYSySnLM9jWGtI.jpg'),
